            <title>Grok vs Google Gemini，AI 改图大比拼</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/24/grok-vs-google-gemini/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=grok-vs-google-gemini</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/24/grok-vs-google-gemini/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 11:59:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Google Gemini]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Grok]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299142</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前小编和大家分享过 Google Gemini 2.0 的改图功能（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/google-gemini-ai-2/ai/">相关教学</a>），最近 Grok 也推出了类似功能，输入简单文字可以替你修改图片。现在就让小编和大家实测一下，到底哪个 AI 改图功能更加强劲。</p><p>以下小编就叫 Grok 和 Gemini 帮小娴戴上太阳眼镜：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299241" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/52544350120_115c18b0-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/52544350120_115c18b0-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/52544350120_115c18b0.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲原图</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299240" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image15-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image15-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image15.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Grok 生成的图片</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299239" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-6-694x462.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-6-694x462.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-6.jpeg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Gemini 生成的图片</p><p>现时在香港使用 Grok 无须 VPN，但如果要试玩 Google Gemini 的话就需要先开启 VPN。</p><p>Grok 网址：<a href="https://x.com/i/grok">https://x.com/i/grok</a></p><p>Google Gemini 2.0 网址：<a href="https://aistudio.google.com/prompts/">https://aistudio.google.com/prompts/</a></p><h2>实测 1：更改衣服颜色</h2><p>小编上传了一张沙律的照片，分别要求 Grok 和 Google Gemini 2.0 将衬衫改为蓝色，看看哪个 AI 生成的结果更好。小编使用的指令为：把衬衫改为蓝色</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299160" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/54022952068_230e5de3-386x580.jpeg" alt="" width="386" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/54022952068_230e5de3-386x580.jpeg 386w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/54022952068_230e5de3.jpeg 599w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 386px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲原图为白色衬衫</p><p>小编首先测试 Grok 的 Edit Image 功能，选择「Edit Image」后，上传小娴的照片并使用「把背心改为红色」指令。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299161" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032445442-694x412.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="412" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032445442-694x412.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032445442.jpg 885w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299166" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032450216-484x580.jpg" alt="" width="484" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032450216-484x580.jpg 484w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032450216.jpg 751w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 484px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Grok 一次会生成 2 个版本供你选择</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299167" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image5-1-386x580.jpg" alt="" width="386" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image5-1-386x580.jpg 386w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image5-1.jpg 599w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 386px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲效果算是自然</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299168" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image6-1-386x580.jpg" alt="" width="386" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image6-1-386x580.jpg 386w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image6-1.jpg 599w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 386px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 但面部却被不明原因修改</p><p>之后小编使用同一照片同一指令，测试 Google Gemini 2.0 的修改图片功能。小编留意到，Google Gemini 2.0 生成速度较 Grok 为慢，而且一次仅可生成一张图片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299162" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032445547-694x400.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="400" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032445547-694x400.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032445547.jpg 746w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299163" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032450049-469x580.jpg" alt="" width="469" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032450049-469x580.jpg 469w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032450049.jpg 727w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 469px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299165" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-2-385x580.jpeg" alt="" width="385" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-2-385x580.jpeg 385w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-2.jpeg 598w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 385px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲衣服颜色有点奇怪，生成得不太自然</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299210" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032464238-620x580.jpg" alt="" width="620" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032464238-620x580.jpg 620w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032464238.jpg 651w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 620px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲颜色过度非常不自然</p><h2>实测 2：更改背景</h2><p>接下来小编上传了一张沙律的相片，分别要求 Grok 和 Google Gemini 2.0 将背景改为沙滩。小编使用的指令为：将背景改为沙滩</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299156" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dscf0731-387x580.jpeg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dscf0731-387x580.jpeg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dscf0731-scaled.jpeg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲原图</p><p>要求 Grok 更改背景后，Grok 生成的图片的确是沙滩，但就更改了沙律的姿势，而且额外为沙律增加了一条丝巾。除此之外亦更改了沙律的样子，完全认不出她。另外放大看的话，可见脚趾非常不自然。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299152" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image4-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image4-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image4.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲更改了原本的姿势</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299211" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image4-1-694x281.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="281" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image4-1-694x281.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image4-1.jpg 1249w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲放大看可见脚趾细节不自然</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299153" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image3-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image3-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image3.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲额外增加了一条丝巾</p><p>与 Grok 相比，Gemini 就可忠实还原沙律本人，但就没有考虑到光暗过渡等问题，感觉像是直接「退地」然后把沙律贴在沙滩上。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299169" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-3-385x580.jpeg" alt="" width="385" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-3-385x580.jpeg 385w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-3.jpeg 598w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 385px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲欠缺光暗处理，失却层次感</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
